{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_04_04",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 04 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "その出来事がきっかけで、琴乃ちゃんもアイドルを\n志すようになったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that incident led Kotono-chan to\naspire to be an idol as well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はっきりなると決めた訳じゃなかったけど……\nそうなれたらって考えるようになったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hadn't made a firm decision to become one‚ but…\nI started to think it would be nice if I could.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あの日以降、また学校に行けるようになったの。でも\n長い間休んでたから授業について行くのが大変で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to go back to school after that day. But\nit was hard to keep up with the classes because I'd been absent for so long…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今の成績のままだと入れる高校はないぞって\n担任の先生に脅されてたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The homeroom teacher even threatened you‚ saying that\nyou wouldn't be able to get into any high school with your current grades.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルになることを考えてたから\n親には中卒でも構わないって言ったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking about becoming an idol‚\nso I told my parents I didn't care if I only graduated middle school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8342626571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらお父さんに凄く怒られて\n高校まではちゃんと卒業するって約束したのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then my dad got really angry‚\nand I promised him I'd at least graduate high school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5675959904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――中学三年のある日の放課後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One afternoon after school‚ during her third year of middle school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2697511037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.7697533925
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.7697533925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは、高校はどこを受験するつもりなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which high school are you planning to take the entrance exam for‚ Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7030867259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.9876445293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "特にこだわりもないし\n行ける所に行くって感じかしら。渚は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't really thought about it.\nI guess I'll just go wherever I can get into. What about you‚ Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1947381654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.3912046273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "星見高校に進学しようと思ってるけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm thinking about going to Hoshimi High School…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3912046273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.1721114636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そう。じゃあ、高校は別々になるわね。寂しくなるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So we'll be going to different high schools. I'll miss you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1721114636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.7235625427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "本当に寂しいと思ってくれてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really mean that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7235625427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.7772586824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前でしょ\n渚とはいつまでも一緒にいたいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI want to be with you forever‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4078442731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.7195942721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……\n決めた！　私、琴乃ちゃんと同じ高校に行く！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…\nI've decided! I'm going to the same high school as you‚ Kotono-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.9333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.1123606843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの。渚はいい高校に行かなきゃダメよ\n私に合わせてレベルを落とすなんて絶対に許さないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? You have to go to a good high school‚ Nagisa.\nI'll never forgive you if you lower your standards just to be with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.443195613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.7266465666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "私にとって「いい高校」は、琴乃ちゃんのいる高校だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me‚ a \"good high school\" is the high school Kotono-chan goes to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7266465666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 102.4235397818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "渚……\n……分かった。だったら、私が星見高校を受験する！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa…\n…Okay. Then I'll take the entrance exam for Hoshimi High School!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0960070131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.9038359327
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.241228763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……！\n星見高校は結構レベル高いけど、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…!\nHoshimi High School is pretty tough‚ are you sure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 121.3101641498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫じゃないけど、渚と同じ高校に行くためだもの\nなんとかするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not sure. But I have to‚\nI have to go to the same high school as you‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2382544038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.9393310708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "だったら私も協力するよ\n一緒に受験勉強して、二人で星見高校に合格しよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll help you.\nLet's study for the exams together‚ and we'll both get into Hoshimi High School!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4666749318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 137.3243906182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "そこから地獄の日々が始まったのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's when the hellish days began.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3743906182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "地獄って……受験がそんなに大変だったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Hellish\"… were the entrance exams that hard?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3496741138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "毎朝早起きして予習して、学校で授業を受けて\n帰って来たら復習して、夜は受験勉強……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I woke up early every morning to study‚ went to school for classes‚\ncame home and reviewed‚ and then studied for the exams at night…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.050035171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "休日は塾に通って、それ以外の日も\n渚に勉強を教えてもらって……本当に大変だったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went to cram school on weekends‚ and even on other days‚\nNagisa tutored me… It was really tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0959050016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "予習復習に受験勉強、塾通いに友達と勉強会……\nそれって普通にみんなやってることじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Reviewing‚ studying for exams‚ cram school‚ study sessions with friends…\nIsn't that what everyone normally does?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.5959050016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "みんなには普通でも、私には大変なことなの！\n間違いなくあの頃が人生で一番勉強していたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be normal for everyone else‚ but it was tough for me!\nThat was definitely the period in my life when I studied the most.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.729234266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんは勉強苦手だもんね\n最後まで頑張り抜いて本当に偉かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan is bad at studying.\nIt was amazing that you persevered until the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.200007248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に合格発表を見に行って\n二人とも合格してた時は手を取り合って喜んだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We went to see the announcement of the successful applicants together‚\nand when we saw that we both passed‚ we held hands and celebrated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.8333405813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "ああいうのを成功体験って言うのかしら\n無理だって言われてた受験がうまくいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if that's what they call a success experience.\nI was told it would be impossible‚ but I passed the entrance exams…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.0337927974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "努力は絶対報われる、頑張れば夢は叶うんだって\n思えるようになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came to believe that\neffort will always be rewarded‚ and that if you work hard‚ your dreams will come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.0004543778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の経験が自信になって、私は決断出来たの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That experience gave me confidence‚ and I was able to make a decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.8292804086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――高校の入学式当日の朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the morning of the high school entrance ceremony.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.3609551752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 220.7276330316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ入学式だね\n琴乃ちゃんとまた同じクラスになれるといいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The entrance ceremony is finally here.\nI hope I'm in the same class as Kotono-chan~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.4666800182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、高校生になったらやってみたいことはある？\n私は琴乃ちゃんと一緒に部活をやってみたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ is there anything you want to do when we become high school students?\nI'd like to join a club with you‚ Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.1201662762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……渚と一緒なら\nきっとどんな部活でも楽しいでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… If it's with you‚ Nagisa‚\nI'm sure any club would be fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.2060317361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "渚……私も高校生になったらやりたいことがあるの\n高校生になったら……私はアイドルになりたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa… I also have something I want to do when we become high school students.\nWhen we're in high school… I want to be an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.5937892352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "……それ、本気なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you serious?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.8411829315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "本気よ。NEXT VENUSグランプリ\n決勝のステージにお姉ちゃんは立てなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am. My sister…\nwasn't able to make it to the final stage of the Next Venus Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.9070290321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "決勝で歌うはずだった特別な曲を\nお姉ちゃんはファンの人達に届けられなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She wasn't able to deliver that special song she was supposed to sing at the finals\nto her fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.2737038368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの心残りを……お姉ちゃんが\n歌えなかった曲を、私がアイドルになって届けたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to become an idol and deliver my sister's unfinished business…\nthe song she couldn't sing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.6070290321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "これが出来るのは……お姉ちゃんの代わりに\nあの曲を歌えるのは、私しかいないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only I can do this…\nOnly I can sing that song in her place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.0403623654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになるのは簡単なことじゃないよ？\n高校受験なんて比じゃないくらい難しいことだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Becoming an idol is not easy‚ you know?\nIt's much‚ much harder than high school entrance exams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.800060145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "分かってる。それでも私はアイドルになりたい……\nううん、ならなきゃいけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. But I still want to be an idol…\nNo‚ I have to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.7381875747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃ちゃんって普段はクールなのに\n時々凄く熱くなるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're usually so cool‚ Kotono-chan‚\nbut sometimes you get so passionate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.4000988006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "そして私は、そういう格好いい琴乃ちゃんが\n大好きなんだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I… I love that about you‚\nthat cool and passionate side of you‚ Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.6001130421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。私も全力で応援する！\n琴乃ちゃんなら絶対アイドルになれるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. I'll support you with all my heart!\nYou can definitely become an idol‚ Kotono-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.0001252491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。渚に応援してもらえたら百人力よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Having your support means the world to me‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.6945048572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "（そうして琴乃ちゃんは、私と過ごす時間を削って）\n（歌やダンスの自主練に取り組むようになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And so‚ Kotono-chan started dedicating more time to）\npracticing singing and dancing on her own.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.833472824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃんが夢中になればなるほど）\n（私と一緒にいられる時間は減って……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The more passionate she became‚）\n（the less time we had together…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.7667959848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_04-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "（応援はしてるけどやっぱり寂しくて……琴乃ちゃんも）\n（麻奈さんに対してこんな気持ちだったのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm supporting her‚ but I still feel lonely… I wonder if Kotono-chan）\nfelt this way towards Mana-san…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.6334524789,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}